LOCUS       pHW_SeqNeutCloni        3982 bp DNA     circular SYN 19-MAR-2026
DEFINITION  Cloning plasmid for barcoded HA segments into duplicated packaging 
            vector (BsmBI sites) for influenza genes under ambisense PolI and 
            PolII promoters to produce both vRNA and mRNA. Updated 2026-04-09
            by Andrew Butler to correct 3 SNPs in ori.
